author: Cameron Glenn
title: Police Investigating Homicide In South Land Park
text:
Sacramento police are investigating a homicide in Sacramento.
There is a heavy police presence on 35 the Avenue in South Land Park. Police there confirm it is a homicide investigation.
This is a developing story.
